title: WOW!: Tootie's April 2016 Mix
description:
Shit is whoa. This mix features Nu Metal, Hip Hop, R&B, various House, and for the first time in a Tootie mix, a Tech House track.

  The Record Company - Off the Ground
  Accept - Balls to the Wall
  Godsmack - Keep Away
  Primer 55 - Loose
  My Darkest Days featuring Zakk Wylde, Chad Kroeger & Tootie - Porn Star Dancing (Tootie Remix)
  Entendre featuring PFV - Rise
  Linkin Park - Papercut
  Methods of Mayhem featuring Kid Rock - New Skin
  Black Rob - Whoa!
  Eminem - Square Dance
  Montell Jordan featuring Master P & Silkk the Shocker - Let's Ride
  Destiny's Child - Where'd You Go
  Mya - Case of the Ex
  Peaches - Rub
  Richard Archon - A Night in Munich
  Deepjack & Andrey Keyton featuring Irina Gi - Give It Back
  Croatia Squad - The D Machine
  Daddy's Groove & Mindshake featuring Kris Kiss - WOW!
  Filatov & Karas featuring Jama - In My Head
  Feder featuring Lyse - Goodbye (DJ Antonio Extended Mix)
  Hardwell & Joey Dale featuring Luciana - Arcadia
  Borgeous & Zaeden - Yesterday
  Lanfranchi & Farina - Sky Meets Bittersweet Symphony

Most tracks are sourced from lossless material. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.

Details:
Format: FLAC, level 7
Length: 1:45:21.752
Average bitrate: 813 kbps
Embedded CUE Sheet
